  "faq": {
    "q1": "How does FIXED work?",
    "a1": "FIXED connects clients with qualified providers for home services. Create a request, a nearby available provider accepts it, and you track the intervention in real time.",
    "q2": "How are providers verified?",
    "a2": "Each provider goes through a verification process: identity documents, professional insurance, and a trade quiz. Only validated profiles can accept missions.",
    "q3": "How do I pay?",
    "a3": "Payment is secured via Stripe. You pay before the mission and the funds are only released to the provider once the mission is complete.",
    "q4": "What if I want to cancel a mission?",
    "a4": "You can cancel a mission from the tracking screen, as long as the provider hasn't started the intervention yet. Refund processed within 3–5 business days.",
    "q5": "How do I contact a provider?",
    "a5": "Once your mission is accepted, you can send a message or call the provider directly from the tracking screen.",
    "q6": "How do I leave a review?",
    "a6": "At the end of each mission, you're invited to rate your provider from 1 to 5 stars and leave a comment. Your reviews help the community.",
    "q7": "How do I withdraw my earnings (providers)?",
    "a7": "From the Wallet tab, submit a withdrawal request. You must first set up your Stripe bank account in your profile."
  },
